VBR MPTS Clock Recovery Enhancement:

- Pick master PCR pid as in CBR case

- Input thread:
  - builds linkage between adjacent PCRs (regardless of program)
  - use adjacent master PCR pairs for average bitrate calculation.

- Output thread: 2 round approach
  - round 1
    - visit all PCRs thru the linkage built by input thread
    - on 1st slave PCR for each program, assign delivery time using the CBR
      model, using the bitrate calculated from master PCR pair
    - on other slave PCRs, use the preceeding PCR in the same program with
      drift adjustment, to determine its delivery time
    - perform necessary error handling if needed

  - round 2
    - visit all TPs again
    - determine non-PCR delivery time, using the PCR delivery times
      with piecewise CBR model

Error handling cases:
  - slave PCR < previous anchor PCR
  - slave PCR > future master PCR
